638
00:38:53.372 --> 00:38:56.042
What are you thinking about?

639
00:38:57.043 --> 00:38:58.794
We're almost there.

640
00:39:05.426 --> 00:39:07.428
I've never been
over here before.

641
00:39:13.392 --> 00:39:17.563
So... you wanna tell me who
that girl was you just had over.

642
00:39:19.648 --> 00:39:22.068
What? No. She's a friend.

643
00:39:24.987 --> 00:39:28.491
I can count on my hand how many
friends you done had over here.

644
00:39:30.451 --> 00:39:32.495
Well. she's one of 'em.

645
00:39:33.162 --> 00:39:35.498
- Mm-hm.
- Mm-hm.

646
00:39:38.292 --> 00:39:41.420
(vocalizing)

647
00:39:41.504 --> 00:39:43.589
♪ ♪

648
00:39:46.425 --> 00:39:48.094
