650
00:39:51.263 --> 00:39:59.263
♪ ♪

651
00:40:34.014 --> 00:40:36.016
Look. Cass. um...

652
00:40:37.268 --> 00:40:39.061
I really like you.

653
00:40:42.731 --> 00:40:45.067
How I wish that things
could be different.

654
00:40:49.655 --> 00:40:52.158
I just think what happened
between us was a mistake.

655
00:40:52.241 --> 00:40:54.368
and we never should
have did what we did.

656
00:40:57.580 --> 00:40:59.206
Yeah. but...

657
00:41:01.375 --> 00:41:03.002
