658
00:41:04.753 --> 00:41:06.046
I shouldn't have. uh...

659
00:41:07.756 --> 00:41:10.593
It was my fault. too.

660
00:41:10.676 --> 00:41:14.054
I just thought... I ju... I just
didn't think that I'd get so. um...

661
00:41:18.976 --> 00:41:22.062
It doesn't matter.
It is what it is.

662
00:41:24.398 --> 00:41:26.025
We can't see each other.

663
00:41:27.484 --> 00:41:30.029
And we can never.
ever speak about this.

664
00:41:35.075 --> 00:41:39.997
I'm so sorry. I'm...
I'm so fuckin' sorry.

665
00:41:46.629 --> 00:41:47.963
(shouts): Cassie!

666
00:41:50.299 --> 00:41:51.509
Cass!

667
00:42:03.187 --> 00:42:04.772
- Lexi Howard.
- Hi.

668
00:42:04.855 --> 00:42:09.026
- How you doin'?
- I'm good. um...

669
00:42:09.109 --> 00:42:13.739
- Hi. I'm Faye.
- I'm Lexi. um...

670
00:42:15.407 --> 00:42:17.409
Are. are you guys...

671
00:42:17.493 --> 00:42:21.330
Fezco: Yeah. no. she's
just stayin' with me for a bit.

672
00:42:21.413 --> 00:42:23.207
but. but she's cool. though.

673
00:42:24.875 --> 00:42:26.794
What brings you out here anyway?

674
00:42:29.213 --> 00:42:31.632
Oh. I just came
to get a. a drink.

675
00:42:35.135 --> 00:42:38.722
Okay. well. we
got plenty of those.

676
00:42:38.806 --> 00:42:42.518
Um... do you need
help finding anything?

677
00:42:43.644 --> 00:42:45.145
No. I'm okay.

678
00:42:45.229 --> 00:42:48.941
Oh. uh. that's the malt liquor.

679
00:42:50.693 --> 00:42:52.027
Yeah. I know.

680
00:42:56.824 --> 00:42:58.200
(car door closes)

681
00:42:58.284 --> 00:43:02.204
(tense music playing)

682
00:43:06.041 --> 00:43:07.376
(car door closes)

683
00:43:14.758 --> 00:43:16.218
Nate: Cassie!

684
00:43:16.302 --> 00:43:18.512
