and he didn't come to the door

748
00:49:48.151 --> 00:49:50.696
to look me in the eye
and shake my hand...

749
00:49:50.779 --> 00:49:52.698
I'd think somethin' was afoot.

750
00:49:52.781 --> 00:49:54.241
O-Okay. but you can't. like.

751
00:49:54.324 --> 00:49:55.826
go in there and start...

752
00:49:55.909 --> 00:50:00.497
- talkin' and stuff. you know?
- Oh shit.

753
00:50:00.580 --> 00:50:04.710
You scared I'mma tell your
mama you're still doin' drugs. huh?

754
00:50:04.793 --> 00:50:07.254
Oh. the anxiety you must have.

755
00:50:07.337 --> 00:50:09.965
(tense music playing)

756
00:50:14.720 --> 00:50:16.388
