759
00:50:34.823 --> 00:50:36.199
Rue: Mom?

760
00:50:36.283 --> 00:50:38.994
(indistinct)

761
00:50:44.040 --> 00:50:45.709
Five minutes. Okay?

762
00:50:45.792 --> 00:50:48.128
What is she gonna
do for five minutes?

763
00:50:49.045 --> 00:50:50.964
Maddy: I don't even wanna know!

764
00:50:52.924 --> 00:50:54.342
(phone buzzing)

